  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个UDP包的结构图，用来给新同事讲解协议格式。标题就叫\"Estructura del paquete UDP\"吧，因为是给拉美团队看的材料。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Estructura del paquete UDP"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好的，packet-beta类型很适合画这种位域结构。UDP头部固定是8字节，对吧？那Data部分的长度应该是可变的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "packet-beta",
        "Data (longitud variable)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，前64位是头部，Data字段长度取决于上层应用。我们按位来划分：0到15位放Source Port，16到31位是Destination Port。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "0-15",
        "Source Port",
        "16-31",
        "Destination Port"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加前两个字段。接下来32到47位应该是Length字段，表示整个UDP报文的长度，包括头部和数据？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "32-47",
        "Length"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Length包含头部8字节。然后48到63位放Checksum，用于校验。最后64位开始就是Data，记得标注\"longitud variable\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "48-63",
        "Checksum",
        "64-95",
        "Data (longitud variable)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。我检查一下：Source Port和Destination Port各占16位，Length和Checksum各16位，Data从64位开始到95位，但实际是变长的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "0-15",
        "16-31",
        "32-47",
        "48-63",
        "64-95"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Data的标注有点问题。西班牙语里\"longitud\"拼写错了，你写的是\"ngitud\"，而且Data的范围不应该固定到95位，它只是示意性的起点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Data (longitud variable)"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "抱歉，我修正一下：Data字段标注为\"Data (longitud variable)\"，拼写正确了。64-95只是示例展示，实际长度由Length字段决定。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Data (longitud variable)",
        "64-95",
        "Length"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "现在对了。这样新同事一眼就能看到UDP头四个固定字段各占多少位，以及数据部分是变长的。可以导出了。",
      "elements_involved": [
